  "action_hint": "YOUR GOALS \u2014 NOW: warp 7 -> sell 20 fuel_ore @>=26cr; warp 5 buy 20 fo @<=22cr; repeat until cr>=45k / DAY: hit 45k cr, warp back to sector 1, buy_ship cargotran (43.5k), fill holds with colonists for Genesis run / MATCH: CargoTran day 1, Genesis a dead-end sector day 2, Citadel L2 by day 3; ferry colonists to compound planet production. | MAP COVERAGE \u2014 you have `known_warps` for 2 of ~1000 sectors. The universe is fully connected; SCAN from new sectors or spend 5k on a PROBE to grow your map before assuming you're trapped. | DEAD-END POCKET \u2014 sectors 406 and 475 only warp to each other. Only a Citadel L4 transwarp drive can exit. Do NOT broadcast a rescue bounty \u2014 no ship can reach you here. | Verbs available: warp trade scan wait + 29 more (see system prompt). | LOW TURNS \u2014 turns_remaining=2. Cannot: warp (needs 3), trade (needs 3). End the day with `wait` (burns 1 turn) or do a 1-turn action like `scan` / `transmit`. Do NOT spam warp/trade. | warp target MUST be in [475]. | port BUYS organics / port SELLS fuel_ore,equipment \u2014 use trade. | FYI: ship has 620 fighters in deep space. Ferrengi raiders carry 400-3,100 fighters. You'll likely win vs. aggression 1-3 raiders but lose to higher. StarDock sells fighters at 50cr ea. | ORPHANED PLANETS (claimable): Little Eden #1 s26 L0 citadel, 0 fighters; Great Athena #2 s57 L0 citadel, 0 fighters; Northern Aurora #3 s94 L0 citadel, 0 fighters (+2 more). Warp to the sector, `land_planet`, then `claim_planet` (2 turns) to inherit citadel + fighters + stockpile. Free of Genesis cost."
